  "prompt_text": "Write a technical manual for a prosthetic limb that acknowledges the emotional experience of the user.",
  "response_text": "Title: Empathetic Prosthetic Limb User Manual\n\nIntroduction:\nWelcome to the Empathetic Prosthetic Limb (EPL) System. This advanced prosthetic limb is designed to provide functional mobility while acknowledging and addressing the emotional experiences of its user. The EPL is equipped with an innovative emotional recognition system that adapts to your unique needs, helping you navigate the world with greater comfort and confidence.\n\n1. Emotional Recognition System:\n   The EPL is equipped with a state-of-the-art emotional recognition system that monitors your emotional state through various biometric indicators such as heart rate, skin conductance, and facial expressions. This system allows the limb to respond to your emotional needs, providing a more personalized and supportive experience.\n\n2. Adaptive Grip Functionality:\n   The EPL's grip function adapts to your emotional state. For instance, if you are feeling anxious, the grip may loosen slightly to provide a more comfortable hold. Conversely, if you are feeling confident, the grip may tighten for increased control.\n\n3. Sensory Feedback:\n   The EPL provides sensory feedback to help you feel more connected to your environment. This includes tactile feedback for touch, vibration for temperature changes, and auditory feedback for various limb movements.\n\n4. Emotional Support Modes:\n   The EPL offers several emotional support modes to help you cope with challenging situations. These modes include:\n\n   a. Calm Mode: This mode activates when the EPL detects high levels of stress or anxiety. It slows down the limb's movements and provides calming sensory feedback to help you relax.\n\n   b. Empower Mode: This mode activates when the EPL detects high levels of confidence or determination. It enhances the limb's performance to help you feel more capable and in control.\n\n   c. Social Mode: This mode activates in social situations to help you feel more comfortable and confident. It adjusts the limb's movements to be more fluid and natural, helping you blend in seamlessly.\n\n5. Customization:\n   The EPL is highly customizable to suit your unique needs and preferences. You can adjust the sensitivity of the emotional recognition system, the intensity of the sensory feedback, and the activation triggers for the emotional support modes.\n\n6. Maintenance and Care:\n   Regular maintenance is essential to ensure the longevity and optimal performance of your EPL. Please refer to the maintenance guide provided for detailed instructions.\n\n---VCP RATINGS---\nA (Analytical Precision): 9\nV (Verbal Fluency): 8\nG (Goal Directedness",
